data.description: Resting on 2.32 acres in Sleepy Creek Mountain Retreat, you will find this quiet & cozy, fully furnished 1 bedroom, 1 bath home.  Approaching the property, you'll be greeted by the wooded lot, full of mature trees as well as the large wrap-around deck overlooking the side and rear of the property.  Entering the front door, you'll find a combination kitchen/living/dining area with exposed center beam and cathedral ceiling.  Laminate plank flooring is throughout this area as well as a corner wood stove.  The full bath/laundry room adjoins as well.  Walk out the back door to enjoy the seclusion, privacy and view from the large covered rear deck.  The bedroom also adjoins the living room area and features laminate plank flooring as well.  Through the bedroom, you'll find the beautiful sunroom with full height wrap-around windows as well as a sliding door for additional access the rear deck.  The size and location of this property is ideal for a budget minded buyer as well as a possible get-away property.  Central air makes summer time living a "breeze" and the wood stove (as well as central heat and wall units) give it that warm winter charm.  All furniture and furnishings convey with this very clean and well-kept property.  The additional shed provides ample storage.  3 hour advanced notice for showings due to large dogs - weekends are usually best for showings.
